      "value": "<p>When you hit a creature with a melee weapon attack, with a weapon with the heavy keyword, you can as a bonus action add your Chakra Strike to the damage roll.</p><p> The target must succeed a Wisdom saving throw, gaining 1 rank of fear on a failed save.</p><p> They can repeat this saving throw at the end of their turns, removing all ranks of fear given by this subclass's abilities.</p><p></p>",
